                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nAlzheimer's disease is a chronic disease with progression of memory deficits over time. The situation presented in the question represents an acute problem. Evaluation is necessary to determine whether hypoglycemia, medication use, or impaired cerebral circulation has had a role in causing the client's current symptoms.",
